Description: The flight into Egypt, after a drawing by Parmigianino Etching printed in brown
Curator's comments: After a drawing by Parmigianino, now lost, but copied in a seventeenth-century drawing in the British Museum (1858,0725,9). (A. E. Popham, Catalogue of Drawings by Parmigianino, 1971, p. 236, no. O.C.21)
Bibliographic references: Weigel 1865 / Die Werke der Maler in ihren Handzeichnungen ; Beschreibendes Verzeichnis der in Kupfer gestochenen, lithographierten und photographierten Facsimiles von Originalzeichnungen grosser Meister (5499)
Acquisition name: Purchased from: A E Evans & Sons
Acquisition notes: Pen and ink inscription on verso 'R Ford'. Not his normal hand but possibly belonged to him.
